      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KAVA QUEEN (5) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing seventh (23.60) last time in a Grade 5 at The Gardens. Solid formlines coming through her last run. Has ability and is a key runner. NUGGET NED (1) showed strong early pace and proved too slick around Bulli over 340m in 19.43, claiming a Grade 5 by one length. One of the key runners again. PEARL OF MAUI (3) turned in a solid run last start over 320m at this track finishing 5th and beaten only 4 lengths (18.58). Should play a prominent role. LUCY VALENTINE (2) was strongly fancied last time but finished third (18.64), beaten 5 lengths. Has a solid record from this box including two wins and a minor placing. Likely to be in the finish again.",
